WEBVTT

00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:15.181
I've made a decision.

00:00:15.266 --> 00:00:18.852
My mother hasn't been well,
she's having some tests.

00:00:19.770 --> 00:00:23.773
I want to be there.
We never see each other, anyway.

00:00:24.275 --> 00:00:26.609
And I need some time to think.

00:00:28.070 --> 00:00:30.530
Call Devasher. She's leaving him.

